results.name: Expansion of (Product_{i=1..m-1} (1 + x^(4*i-1))) * (1 + x^(2*m-1)) for m = 12.
comment: (Product_{i=1..m-1} (1 + x^(4*i-1))) * (1 + x^(2*m-1)) is the Poincaré polynomial for O(2m).
reference: H. Weyl, The Classical Groups, Princeton, 1946, see p. 238.
